<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/room.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/modal.css">

    <!-- Fonts  -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans&family=Poppins:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"rel="stylesheet">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Criar Sala - Rocket.Q</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="room" class="content">

        <header>
            <img src="./images/logo.svg" alt="Rocket.Q Logo">
            <div class="buttons">
                <button class="button outline">
                    #323243
                    <img src="./images/copy.svg" alt="Copiar">
                </button>
                <button class="button">
                    <img src="./images/users-white.svg" alt="Copiar">
                    Criar sala
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section id="questions-form">
                <h2>Faça sua pergunta</h2>
                <form action="">
                    <label class="sr-only" for-id="quention">O que você quer perguntar?</label>
                    <textarea name="quention" id="quention" placeholder="O que você quer perguntar?"></textarea>
                    <footer>
                        <div class="lock">
                            <img src="./images/locker.svg" alt="Cadeado">
                            Esta pergunta é anônima
                        </div>

                        <button class="button">
                            Enviar
                        </button>
                    </footer>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section id="questions">
                <h2 class="sr-only">Perguntas da comunidade</h2>
                <div class="question-wrapper">
                    <div class="question-content">
                        <div class="question-user"><img src="./images/user.svg" alt="Avatar"></div>
                        <div class="question">
                            <p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim fugiat aliquam at eos ab aperiam, ea assumenda consequatur nemo porro earum. Necessitatibus a amet officia est voluptatum molestiae consequatur quam! Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim fugiat aliquam at eos ab aperiam, ea assumenda consequatur nemo porro earum. Necessitatibus a amet officia est voluptatum molestiae consequatur quam! Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Enim fugiat aliquam at eos ab aperiam, ea assumenda consequatur nemo porro earum. Necessitatibus a amet officia est voluptatum molestiae consequatur quam!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="question-actions">
                        <div><a href="#"><img src="./images/vector.svg" alt="Marcar como lida">Marcar como lida</a></div>
                        <div><a href="#"><img src="./images/trash.svg" alt="Excluir">Excluir</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="question-wrapper">
                    <div class="question-content">
                        <div class="question-user"><img src="./images/user.svg" alt="Avatar"></div>
                        <div class="question">
                            <p>O que é TypeScript?</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="question-actions">
                        <div><a href="#"><img src="./images/vector.svg" alt="Marcar como lida">Marcar como lida</a></div>
                        <div><a href=""><img src="./images/trash.svg" alt="Excluir">Excluir</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="question-wrapper read">
                    <div class="question-content">
                        <div class="question-user"><img src="./images/user.svg" alt="Avatar"></div>
                        <div class="question">
                            <p>Qual a diferença entre const, var e let no javascript?</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="question-actions">
                        <div><a href="#"><img src="./images/vector.svg" alt="Marcar como lida">Pergunta lida</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
    <!-- Modal -->

    <div class="modal-wrapper">
        <div class="modal">
            <h2>Excluir Pergunta</h2>
            <p>Tem certeza que você deseja excluir esta pergunta?</p>

            <form action="">
                <label class="sr-only" for-id="password-delete">Insira a senha</label>
                <input type="password" placeholder="Insira a senha">
                <div class="buttons">
                    <button class="button-grey">Cancelar</button>
                    <button class="button-red">Sim, excluir</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>